### 1. Tüm Mürettebatı Getir (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/crew-service/api/crews

###

### 2. Yeni Mürettebat Ekle (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/crew-service/api/crews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vehbi Hürkuş",
  "role": "ENGINEER",
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

###

### 3. Durumu Güncelle (PUT) - Not: ID numarasını 4 kabul ettim, gerekirse değiştir
PUT http://localhost:8080/crew-service/api/crews/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mehmet Kum",
  "role": "ENGINEER",
  "status": "ON_FLIGHT"
}

###

### 4. Kaydı Sil (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/crew-service/api/crews/4